Lyric:
[by:赵轱辘]
[00:00.86]The love, the love
[00:06.03]The love, the love
[00:11.58]The love, the love
[00:16.54]The love
[00:22.81]Time is all-forgiven
[00:30.95]Tell me how it ends
[00:36.07]Cause no one knows me quite like you do
[00:44.02]And these conversations in my head
[00:46.91]Turn into the words that you never said
[00:49.77]Oh no, oh no, oh no
[00:54.90]I hold it inside not to fall apart
[00:57.76]How many ways can we restart?
[01:00.59]And this weird life living
[01:08.75]Is pulling me away
[01:11.40]Constant craving
[01:14.18]Is more than I can take
[01:16.37]And maybe I don’t want this
[01:19.45]No, I would give it up for
[01:23.58]Love
[01:27.67]So just wait, follow me back
[01:35.97]Know at times I can get sidetrack
[01:41.40]All this space just leads me back to you
[01:49.39]And these conversations in my head
[01:52.33]Turn into the words that you never said
[01:54.62]Oh no, oh no, oh no
[02:00.30]I hold it inside not to fall apart
[02:03.21]How many ways can we restart?
[02:11.13]And this weird life living
[02:14.20]Is pulling me away
[02:16.87]Constant craving
[02:19.57]Is more than I can take
[02:21.66]And maybe I don’t want this
[02:25.02]No, I would give it up for
[02:28.30]Love
[02:33.41]Let’s not leave it to chance
[02:35.84]We can’t blame circumstance
[02:38.50]Cause in this life there’s no certainty
[02:44.06]And it’s all one result
[02:46.80]Who knows where this will go
[02:49.54]It’s more than we can understand
[02:54.82]And this weird life living
[02:57.76]Is pulling me away
[03:00.40]Constant craving
[03:03.24]Is more than I can take
[03:05.28]And maybe I don’t want this
[03:08.62]No, I would give it up for
[03:11.70]Love
[03:17.35]
